en-US.title: UCHS Vine Hill Clinic
en-US.description: UCHS Vine Hill Clinic is a medical clinic serving the Nashville community, including the transgender folks. Our professional staff is empathetic, patient-centered, and experienced in handling health-related concerns, including chronic ailments. We have a wonderful Spanish speaking staff, ensuring we cater to a diverse patient population. Our informed-consent-clinic supports transgender individuals' healthcare needs and promotes their well-being
